  "detailed_description": "A small adventure metroidvania game, where you playing as our-time teenager, who was summoned by wizard in fantasy world! And that wizard gave him a quest - return stolen king's treasures! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022010/extras/95b4cf441fdca62c2314cf623d898131.poster.avif?t=1571220842\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022010/extras/95b4cf441fdca62c2314cf623d898131.webm?t=1571220842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022010/extras/95b4cf441fdca62c2314cf623d898131.mp4?t=1571220842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong><br>- There's no autosaves or custom saves, you can save your progress only near checkpoints<br>- Open world! You can go wherever you want (and can, surely, he-he-he) in this dungeon<br>- A lot of upgrades, that can help you open new parts on dungeon and make you way easily<br>- BIG BOSSES!<br>- Retro style (pixel art and 8-bit music)<br>- Tons of secrets!<br>- Only awesome gameplay! No boring dialogues! No stupid empty rooms! No hard lvl-up systems and anything like that! ONLY! AWESOME! GAMEPLAY!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022010/extras/c0a961261bb835bdfd5c94fa9f27f82f.poster.avif?t=1571220842\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022010/extras/c0a961261bb835bdfd5c94fa9f27f82f.webm?t=1571220842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022010/extras/c0a961261bb835bdfd5c94fa9f27f82f.mp4?t=1571220842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
